                <h1>Gluten-free needs pose challenges</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/ee203faf-a295-4301-b08a-e5d9f0359937.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="The&#x20;number&#x20;of&#x20;students&#x20;requesting&#x20;special&#x20;gluten-free&#x20;diets&#x20;has&#x20;doubled&#x20;in&#x20;the&#x20;last&#x20;few&#x20;years,&#x20;said&#x20;Franca&#x20;Alphin,&#x20;director&#x20;of&#x20;nutrition&#x20;services&#x20;at&#x20;Student&#x20;Health." class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            The number of students requesting special gluten-free diets has doubled in the last few years, said Franca Alphin, director of nutrition services at Student Health.

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
